    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } P(H_1) = \\frac{C_5^2}{C_{12}^2} = \\frac{5}{33}; P(H_2) = \\frac{C_7^2}{C_{12}^2} = \\frac{7}{22}; P(H_3) = \\frac{C_5^1 C_7^1}{C_{12}^2} = \\frac{35}{66}.\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      156,
