    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Ta có: } P(A|H_1) = \\frac{12}{27}; P(A|H_2) = \\frac{10}{27}; P(A|H_3) = \\frac{11}{27}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
